'''二氧化铌'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为NbO<sub>2</sub>。它是一种深蓝色固体，也是一种[[非整比化合物|非整比化合物]]，铌氧比例在 NbO<sub>1.94</sub>-NbO<sub>2.09</sub> 之间。<ref name = "Gupta"/>

==制备与结构==

二氧化铌可以由Nb<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub> 和H<sub>2</sub>在800–1350 °C 反应而成。<ref name = "Gupta"/> 另一种方法是[[五氧化二铌|Nb<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub>]] 和金属铌在 1100 °C 发生的归中反应。<ref name = "Patnaik">Pradyot Patnaik (2002), ''Handbook of Inorganic Chemicals'',McGraw-Hill Professional, {{ISBN|0-07-049439-8}}</ref>在工业生产金属铌时，NbO<sub>2</sub>会作为[[五氧化二铌|Nb<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub>]]氢气还原过程中的中间体出现。<ref name = "Schnitter">Patent EP1524252, Sintered bodies based on niobium suboxide, Schnitter C, Wötting G</ref> NbO<sub>2</sub> 会和镁蒸汽反应，生成铌金属。<ref>Method for producing tantalum/niobium metal powders by the reduction of their oxides by gaseous magnesium, US patent 6171363 (2001), Shekhter L.N., Tripp T.B., Lanin L.L. (H. C. Starck, Inc.)</ref>

在室温， NbO<sub>2</sub> 会形成[[四方晶系|四方晶系]]，[[金红石|金红石]]结构。它的 Nb-Nb 距离较短。<ref>Wells A.F. (1984) ''Structural Inorganic Chemistry'' 5th edition Oxford Science Publications {{ISBN|0-19-855370-6}}</ref> 高温下的二氧化铌也会形成类似[[二氧化钛|金红石]]结构的晶体。它们的 Nb-Nb 距离也很短。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1006/jssc.1994.1334|title=A Powder Neutron Diffraction Study of Semiconducting and Metallic Niobium Dioxide|year=1994|author=Bolzan, A|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=113|issue=1|pages=9–14|last2=Fong|first2=Celesta|last3=Kennedy|first3=Brendan J.|last4=Howard|first4=Christopher J.|bibcode = 1994JSSCh.113....9B }}</ref>

据报道，二氧化铌有两个高压相，其中一个具有金红石结构，也具有短的Nb-Nb距离；另一种具有与{{le|斜锆石|baddeleyite}}类似的结构，在更高压力下出现。 <ref>{{cite journal| doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.59.13650| title=High-pressure structural phase transitions in semiconducting niobium dioxide| year=1999|author1=Haines, J. |author2=Léger, J. M. |author3=Pereira, A. S. | journal=Physical Review B| volume=59| pages=13650| issue=21 |bibcode = 1999PhRvB..5913650H | hdl=10183/198788|}}</ref>

==性质==
NbO<sub>2</sub> 不溶于水，是一种强还原剂，可以还原[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]成碳单质，把[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]]还原成硫单质。<ref name = "Gupta"/>

高温下[[氨|氨]]解NbO<sub>2</sub>，可以得到氮化物Nb<sub>0.84</sub>N。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Zeitschrift für Naturforschung B|volume=66|issue=1|issn=1865-7117|date=2011-01-01|pages=1–6|doi=10.1515/znb-2011-0101|url=https://www.degruyter.com/view/journals/znb/66/1/article-p1.xml|title=Synthesis and Crystal Structure of Nb0.84N|accessdate=2020-07-19|author=Nancy Frenzel, Elisabeth Irran, Martin Lerch, Alexandra Buchsteiner}}</ref>NbO<sub>2</sub>和BaCO<sub>3</sub>在CS<sub>2</sub>中硫化，可以得到BaNbS<sub>3-δ</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Materials Research Bulletin|volume=30|issue=4|language=en|date=1995-04|pages=463–469|doi=10.1016/0025-5408(95)00012-7|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0025540895000127|title=The preparation and characterization of low-dimensional BaNbS3 − δ|accessdate=2020-07-19|author=J. Yan, K.V. Ramanujachary, M. Greenblatt|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630153010/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0025540895000127|dead-url=no}}</ref>

